s.'),(1832,318,'_get_evaluated','field_5464e476a976d'),(1833,318,'get_discovered','This is your chance to get discovered, just like the thousands of players from across the country that started their path to greatness at our tryouts. '),(1834,318,'_get_discovered','field_5464e487a976e'),(1835,318,'get_recruited','With our Premium Video Package, your tryout video can be seen by thousands of college coaches from around the country. '),(1836,318,'_get_recruited','field_5464e493a976f'),(1837,318,'arm_speed','70'),(1838,318,'_arm_speed','field_5464e4c217fbf'),(1839,318,'bat_speed','77'),(1840,318,'_bat_speed','field_5464e4d117fc0'),(1841,318,'60_yard_dash','6.7'),(1842,318,'_60_yard_dash','field_5464e4d517fc1'),(1843,318,'gold_glove','The best ballplayers start at The Factory.\r\nBaseball Factory alum have won two MVP awards, five Cy Youngs, Four Rookie of the Year awards, 24 Gold Gloves, and 33 Silver Sluggers. '),(1844,318,'_gold_glove','field_5464e500edf30'),(1845,315,'event_intro',''),(1846,315,'_event_intro','field_5464e2b42270b'),(1847,315,'event_content','Over the last 20+ years, thousands of Baseball Factory players have made college teams and hundreds have played in the MLB, including Justin Verlander, CC Sabathia, and David Wright. All players get their start at an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout. And on Monday, February 16 it’s your turn to be discovered.'),(1848,315,'_event_content','field_5464e3437f7d0'),(1849,315,'player_img','328'),(1850,315,'_player_img','field_5464e377328c9'),(1851,315,'player_quote','\"Baseball Factory helped me improve my game and allowed me to play in front of all the right people.\" '),(1852,315,'_player_quote','field_5464e399328ca'),(1853,315,'get_evaluated','Our professional coaches evaluate your skills and help you improve your game while showing you how you stack up against other players.'),(1854,315,'_get_evaluated','field_5464e476a976d'),(1855,315,'get_discovered','This is your chance to get discovered, just like the thousands of players from across the country that started their path to greatness at our tryouts. '),(1856,315,'_get_discovered','field_5464e487a976e'),(1857,315,'get_recruited','With our Premium Video Package, your tryout video can be seen by thousands of college coaches from around the country. '),(1858,315,'_get_recruited','field_5464e493a976f'),(1859,315,'arm_speed','70'),(1860,315,'_arm_speed','field_5464e4c217fbf'),(1861,315,'bat_speed','77'),(1862,315,'_bat_speed','field_5464e4d117fc0'),(1863,315,'60_yard_dash','6.7'),(1864,315,'_60_yard_dash','field_5464e4d517fc1'),(1865,315,'gold_glove','The best ballplayers start at The Factory.\r\nBaseball Factory alum have won two MVP awards, five Cy Youngs, Four Rookie of the Year awards, 24 Gold Gloves, and 33 Silver Sluggers. '),(1866,315,'_gold_glove','field_5464e500edf30'),(1867,319,'_edit_lock','1415917591:4'),(1868,319,'_edit_last','4'),(1869,319,'event_intro',''),(1870,319,'_event_intro','field_5464e2b42270b'),(1871,319,'event_content','Over the last 20+ years, thousands of Baseball Factory players have made college teams and hundreds have played in the MLB, including 7-time All-Star David Wright. Like David, all players get their start at an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout. And on Saturday, March 7 it’s your turn to be discovered.'),(1872,319,'_event_content','field_5464e3437f7d0'),(1873,319,'player_img','328'),(1874,319,'_player_img','field_5464e377328c9'),(1875,319,'player_quote','“My road to the pros started at a Baseball Factory tryout.”'),(1876,319,'_player_quote','field_5464e399328ca'),(1877,319,'get_evaluated','“Baseball Factory gave me an honest, constructive evaluation that helped me improve my hitting, fielding, and throwing skills.”'),(1878,319,'_get_evaluated','field_5464e476a976d'),(1879,319,'get_discovered','“I had the chance to play alongside great talent and play in front of professional scouts from around the country.”'),(1880,319,'_get_discovered','field_5464e487a976e'),(1881,319,'get_recruited','“With the Premium Video Program, my tryout video could be seen by thousands of coaches from great colleges.”'),(1882,319,'_get_recruited','field_5464e493a976f'),(1883,319,'arm_speed','65'),(1884,319,'_arm_speed','field_5464e4c217fbf'),(1885,319,'bat_speed','72'),(1886,319,'_bat_speed','field_5464e4d117fc0'),(1887,319,'60_yard_dash','7.1'),(1888,319,'_60_yard_dash','field_5464e4d517fc1'),(1889,319,'gold_glove','For David Wright, his experience on the Baseball Factory All-America team helped him go from good fielder to Gold Glove winner. Through superior coaching and lots of hard work, David became one of the best fielding third basemen in the game. '),(1890,319,'_gold_glove','field_5464e500edf30'),(1895,321,'_edit_lock','1415997038:4'),(1896,321,'_edit_last','4'),(1897,321,'field_5465178d42959','a:11:{s:3:\"key\";s:19:\"field_5465178d42959\";s:5:\"label\";s:17:\"Page Introduction\";s:4:\"name\";s:10:\"page_intro\";s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"wysiwyg\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"default_value\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"toolbar\";s:4:\"full\";s:12:\"media_upload\";s:3:\"yes\";s:17:\"conditional_logic\";a:3:{s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"rules\";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:5:\"field\";s:4:\"null\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"allorany\";s:3:\"all\";}s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;}'),(1899,321,'position','acf_after_title'),(1900,321,'layout','no_box'),(1901,321,'hide_on_screen',''),(1902,56,'page_intro',''),(1903,56,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(1904,63,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Teams</strong></h1>\r\nAs a member of an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Team, you receive highly accelerated training from our professional coaches, play in tournaments against some of the best players in the country, and get national exposure to college coaches.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to make our teams?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(1905,63,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(1906,323,'page_intro','&lt;h1&gt;UA &lt;strong&gt;Baseball Factory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;\r\nBaseball Factory and Under Armour have joined forces to discover and develop the best high school baseball players in the country.\r\n\r\nIt all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour where players are evaluated by our professional instructors. Top players are then invited to attend National Team, National Training, and All-America events. There they receive high-level instruction, compete against other top prospects, and play in front of college coaches.\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"#events\"&gt;Explore Opportunities&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;'),(1907,323,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(1908,13,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour <strong>Baseball Factory</strong></h1>\r\nBaseball Factory and Under Armour have joined forces to discover and develop the best high school baseball players in the country.\r\n\r\nIt all starts at the <a href=\"http://fa.drxlrdev.com/events/\">Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour</a> where players are evaluated by our professional instructors. Top players are then invited to attend Under Armour Baseball Factory National Team, National Training, and All-America events. There they receive high-level instruction, compete against other top prospects, and play in front of college coaches.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#events\">Explore Opportunities</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(1909,13,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(1910,316,'field_54651d90bf9f7','a:14:{s:3:\"key\";s:19:\"field_54651d90bf9f7\";s:5:\"label\";s:11:\"Player Name\";s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"player_name\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"text\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"default_value\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"placeholder\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"prepend\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"append\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"formatting\";s:4:\"html\";s:9:\"maxlength\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"conditional_logic\";a:3: