At Baseball Factory, our results speak for themselves.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n1 out of every 4 players drafted into professional baseball have trained with Baseball Factory\r\n\r\n3,500+ Baseball Factory players have been selected in the MLB draft\r\n\r\n350+ Baseball Factory alumni have gone on to play in the Big Leagues including CC Sabathia, Roy Halladay, Mark Teixeira and David Wright\r\n\r\n99% of Division I college baseball programs have at least one Baseball Factory alum on their rosters\r\n\r\n70% of Division II college baseball programs have at least one Baseball Factory alum on their rosters\r\n\r\n60% of Division III college baseball programs have at least one Baseball Factory alum on their rosters\r\n\r\n1 out of every 4 players from last year\'s College World Series is a Baseball Factory alum\r\n\r\n$1 Billion+ in college scholarships have been acquired for our players\r\n\r\n50,000+ of our student-athletes have successfully graduated from college'),(2039,359,'_results','field_54662cf304b1c'),(2040,21,'results','<h3>The Proof is in the Results</h3>\r\nAt Baseball Factory, our results speak for themselves.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n1 out of every 4 players drafted into professional baseball have trained with Baseball Factory\r\n\r\n3,500+ Baseball Factory players have been selected in the MLB draft\r\n\r\n350+ Baseball Factory alumni have gone on to play in the Big Leagues including CC Sabathia, Roy Halladay, Mark Teixeira and David Wright\r\n\r\n99% of Division I college baseball programs have at least one Baseball Factory alum on their rosters\r\n\r\n70% of Division II college baseball programs have at least one Baseball Factory alum on their rosters\r\n\r\n60% of Division III college baseball programs have at least one Baseball Factory alum on their rosters\r\n\r\n1 out of every 4 players from last year\'s College World Series is a Baseball Factory alum\r\n\r\n$1 Billion+ in college scholarships have been acquired for our players\r\n\r\n50,000+ of our student-athletes have successfully graduated from college'),(2041,21,'_results','field_54662cf304b1c'),(2042,360,'page_intro','[don\'t think we need this page since Results is on the main About page - CW]'),(2043,360,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2044,75,'page_intro','[don\'t think we need this page since Results is on the main About page - CW]'),(2045,75,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2046,361,'page_intro','<h1>Our Company History</h1>\r\nBaseball Factory was founded in 1994 by CEO Steve Sclafani to provide a service that would advise and educate players on the college recruiting process. It is Baseball Factory\'s goal to provide baseball players nationwide with a one-of-a-kind concept that provides the very best in instruction, tournament competition, and college planning and promotion. Baseball Factory\'s vision is to guide both players and parents through the college recruiting process and to professionally train players in order to find a school that is the right fit...both academically and athletically.\r\n\r\nBaseball Factory is widely recognized as a leader in player development and college placement in the U.S.  The unique combination of pro evaluations, fully edited player videos, professional instruction, tournaments, and ongoing guidance has created college placement success stories for thousands of players.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.teamonebaseball.com/\">Team One Baseball</a>\r\n\r\nIn 2004, Baseball Factory acquired Team One Baseball, a company renowned for organizing elite showcase events across the country. At these select nationwide events, top high school talent is showcased for over 100 college coaches and professional scouts. Through this joint association, Baseball Factory’s players not only receive quality training and guidance, but also the kind of exposure essential for success at the next level. The results are undeniable. Together Baseball Factory and Team One have helped players secure over $1 Billion in college scholarships. Over 3,000 Baseball Factory and Team One alumni have been selected in the MLB amateur draft and over 320 of these players have suited up for a Major League team.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBaseball Factory &amp; Team One Foundation\r\n\r\nIt is the vision of Baseball Factory to professionally train players and guide families through the college recruiting process in order to find a school that is the right fit... both academically and athletically. In line with that vision, Baseball Factory has been providing assistance to at-need youth in Baltimore City for the past 14 years. Seeking to expand that support to a national level, Baseball Factory recently formed the Baseball Factory and Team One Foundation.\r\n\r\nIt is the mission of the Baseball Factory and Team One Foundation to help young players, who might otherwise be unable to pay for recruiting services, benefit from guidance and training for the college recruitment process. The Foundation hopes to offer three primary options to help disadvantaged young players through Baseball Factory programs: Instructional Days, Scholarships for Participation in Baseball Factory and Team One Programs, and Scholarships for College.'),(2047,361,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2048,77,'page_intro','<h1>Our Company History</h1>\r\nBaseball Factory was founded in 1994 by CEO Steve Sclafani to provide a service that would advise and educate players on the college recruiting process. It is Baseball Factory\'s goal to provide baseball players nationwide with a one-of-a-kind concept that provides the very best in instruction, tournament competition, and college planning and promotion. Baseball Factory\'s vision is to guide both players and parents through the college recruiting process and to professionally train players in order to find a school that is the right fit...both academically and athletically.\r\n\r\nBaseball Factory is widely recognized as a leader in player development and college placement in the U.S.  The unique combination of pro evaluations, fully edited player videos, professional instruction, tournaments, and ongoing guidance has created college placement success stories for thousands of players.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.teamonebaseball.com/\">Team One Baseball</a>\r\n\r\nIn 2004, Baseball Factory acquired Team One Baseball, a company renowned for organizing elite showcase events across the country. At these select nationwide events, top high school talent is showcased for over 100 college coaches and professional scouts. Through this joint association, Baseball Factory’s players not only receive quality training and guidance, but also the kind of exposure essential for success at the next level. The results are undeniable. Together Baseball Factory and Team One have helped players secure over $1 Billion in college scholarships. Over 3,000 Baseball Factory and Team One alumni have been selected in the MLB amateur draft and over 320 of these players have suited up for a Major League team.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBaseball Factory &amp; Team One Foundation\r\n\r\nIt is the vision of Baseball Factory to professionally train players and guide families through the college recruiting process in order to find a school that is the right fit... both academically and athletically. In line with that vision, Baseball Factory has been providing assistance to at-need youth in Baltimore City for the past 14 years. Seeking to expand that support to a national level, Baseball Factory recently formed the Baseball Factory and Team One Foundation.\r\n\r\nIt is the mission of the Baseball Factory and Team One Foundation to help young players, who might otherwise be unable to pay for recruiting services, benefit from guidance and training for the college recruitment process. The Foundation hopes to offer three primary options to help disadvantaged young players through Baseball Factory programs: Instructional Days, Scholarships for Participation in Baseball Factory and Team One Programs, and Scholarships for College.'),(2049,77,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2050,77,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Baseball Factory Company History'),(2051,77,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Since 1994, Baseball Factory has helped thousands of top baseball prospects play in college and hundreds make it to the Majors.'),(2052,363,'page_intro','<h1>Baseball Factory Alumni</h1>\r\nOur proven program of training, evaluation, and college recruiting guidance has helped many student-athletes achieve their goals of playing college and professional baseball. Our alumni include MVP, Cy Young, Rookie of the Year and Gold Glove award winners, along with more than 350 MLB players and more than 50,000 college ballplayers.'),(2053,363,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2054,83,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Baseball Factory Alumni | Under Armour | Baseball Prospects'),(2055,83,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Our alumni include MVP, Cy Young, Rookie of the Year and Gold Glove award winners, along with 350+ MLB players and more than 50,000 college ballplayers.'),(2056,83,'page_intro','<h1>Baseball Factory Alumni</h1>\r\nOur proven program of training, evaluation, and college recruiting guidance has helped many student-athletes achieve their goals of playing college and professional baseball. Our alumni include MVP, Cy Young, Rookie of the Year and Gold Glove award winners, along with more than 350 MLB players and more than 50,000 college ballplayers.'),(2057,83,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2058,364,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction and personal attention from our experienced coaching staff that includes current and former professional players, college coaches, and pro scouts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to participate?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2059,364,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2060,365,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction and personal attention from our experienced coaching staff that includes current and former professional players, college coaches, and pro scouts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to participate?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2061,365,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2062,366,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction and personal attention from our experienced coaching staff that includes current and former professional players, college coaches, and pro scouts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to participate?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2063,366,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2064,321,'field_546666ec96aa6','a:11:{s:3:\"key\";s:19:\"field_546666ec96aa6\";s:5:\"label\";s:12:\"Page Excerpt\";s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"page_excerpt\";s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"wysiwyg\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"default_value\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"toolbar\";s:4:\"full\";s:12:\"media_upload\";s:3:\"yes\";s:17:\"conditional_logic\";a:3:{s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"rules\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"field\";s:4:\"null\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";}}s:8:\"allorany\";s:3:\"all\";}s:8:\"order_no\";i:1;}'),(2065,321,'rule','a:5:{s:5:\"param\";s:9:\"post_type\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:4:\"page\";s:8:\"order_no\";i:0;s:8:\"group_no\";i:0;}'),(2066,367,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction an