,369,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2078,369,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Training</h2>\r\nOur training camps offer intense instruction to enhance your game.'),(2079,369,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2080,370,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction and personal attention from our experienced coaching staff that includes current and former professional players, college coaches, and pro scouts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to participate?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2081,370,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2082,370,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Training</h2>\r\nOur training camps offer intense instruction\r\nto enhance your game.'),(2083,370,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2084,371,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Teams</strong></h1>\r\nAs a member of an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Team, you receive highly accelerated training from our professional coaches, play in tournaments against some of the best players in the country, and get national exposure to college coaches.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to make our teams?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2085,371,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2086,371,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Teams</h2>\r\nGet top-level coaching and compete on our tournament teams.'),(2087,371,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2088,63,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Teams</h2>\r\nGet top-level coaching and compete\r\non our tournament teams.'),(2089,63,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2090,372,'page_intro','Under Armour All-America Game\r\n\r\nThis is the definitive gathering of baseball elite. The Under Armour All-America Game is powered by Baseball Factory and returns to Wrigley Field this summer.'),(2091,372,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2092,372,'page_excerpt','This is the definitive gathering of high school baseball elite.'),(2093,372,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2094,67,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> All-America Game</h2>\r\nThis is the definitive gathering of\r\nhigh school baseball elite.'),(2095,67,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2096,373,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory Preseason Tournament</h1>\r\nThis is your opportunity to play in front of All-America Game scouts. Our scouts will evaluate 2016 and 2017 grads for selection to the Under Armour All-America Game, which returns to historic Wrigley Field this summer.\r\n\r\nJanuary 16–18 / Cubs Park / Mesa, AZ'),(2097,373,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2098,373,'page_excerpt','28 teams vie for this prestigious tournament championship.'),(2099,373,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2100,69,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> Pre-season Tourney</h2>\r\n28 teams vie for this prestigious\r\ntournament championship.'),(2101,69,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2102,374,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory All-America Preseason Rookie Tournament</h1>\r\nJanuary 16-18 / Lake Myrtle Sports Complex / Auburndale, FL'),(2103,374,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2104,374,'page_excerpt','Showcase your skills alongside other All-American pre-season rookies.'),(2105,374,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2106,71,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> Pre-season Rookies</h2>\r\nShowcase your skills alongside other\r\nAll-American pre-season rookies.'),(2107,71,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2108,375,'page_intro','<h1>Meet Our Team</h1>\r\nIt takes a great team to make Baseball Factory a valuable program for our student-athletes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Need:</strong>\r\n\r\n<i>Filterable </i><a href=\"http://www.baseballfactory.com/aboutus/meetthestaff.asp\"><i>staff list</i></a><i> that includes the following for each:</i>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i><i>Name</i></i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Title</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Bio</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Headshot</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Group (executive team, baseball operations, etc.)</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(2109,375,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2110,375,'page_excerpt','It takes a great team to make Baseball Factory a valuable program for our student-athletes.'),(2111,375,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2112,79,'page_excerpt','<h2>Meet Our Team</h2>\r\nIt takes a great team to make Baseball Factory a valuable program for our student-athletes.'),(2113,79,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2114,376,'page_intro','<h1>Meet Our Team</h1>\r\nIt takes a great team to make Baseball Factory a valuable program for our student-athletes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Need:</strong>\r\n\r\n<i>Filterable </i><a href=\"http://www.baseballfactory.com/aboutus/meetthestaff.asp\"><i>staff list</i></a><i> that includes the following for each:</i>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i><i>Name</i></i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Title</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Bio</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Headshot</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Group (executive team, baseball operations, etc.)</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(2115,376,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2116,376,'page_excerpt','<h2>Meet Our Team</h2>\r\nIt takes a great team to make Baseball Factory a valuable program for our student-athletes.'),(2117,376,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2118,377,'page_intro','<h1>What Factory Fans Have to Say...</h1>\r\nThousands of athletes, parents, and coaches around the country are fans of Baseball Factory. Read why they love our program, in their own words.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[need content field to add testimonials with categories]'),(2119,377,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2120,377,'page_excerpt','<h2>Factory Fans</h2>\r\nThousands of athletes, parents, and coaches around the country are fans of Baseball Factory.'),(2121,377,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2122,81,'page_excerpt','<h2>Factory Fans</h2>\r\nThousands of athletes, parents, and coaches around the country are fans of Baseball Factory.'),(2123,81,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2124,378,'page_intro','As the leaders in baseball player development and college promotion, Baseball Factory instructs and scouts more than 20,000 players every year. In partnership with Under Armour, we go through a rigorous process to evaluate and rank the top 100 high school prospects in the country. These are the Top 100.'),(2125,378,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2126,378,'page_excerpt','<h2>The Top 100</h2>\r\nAs the leaders in baseball player development and college promotion, Baseball Factory instructs and scouts more than 20,000 players every year. In partnership with Under Armour, we go through a rigorous process to evaluate and rank the top 100 high school prospects in the country.'),(2127,378,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2128,48,'page_excerpt','<h2>The Top 100</h2>\r\nAs the leaders in baseball player development and college promotion, Baseball Factory instructs and scouts more than 20,000 players every year. In partnership with Under Armour, we go through a rigorous process to evaluate and rank the top 100 high school prospects in the country.'),(2129,48,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2130,379,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Teams</strong></h1>\r\nAs a member of an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Team, you receive highly accelerated training from our professional coaches, play in tournaments against some of the best players in the country, and get national exposure to college coaches.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to make our teams?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2131,379,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2132,379,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Teams</h2>\r\nGet top-level coaching and compete\r\non our tournament teams.'),(2133,379,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2134,380,'page_intro','Under Armour All-America Game\r\n\r\nThis is the definitive gathering of baseball elite. The Under Armour All-America Game is powered by Baseball Factory and returns to Wrigley Field this summer.'),(2135,380,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2136,380,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> All-America Game</h2>\r\nThis is the definitive gathering of\r\nhigh school baseball elite.'),(2137,380,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2138,381,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory All-America Preseason Rookie Tournament</h1>\r\nJanuary 16-18 / Lake Myrtle Sports Complex / Auburndale, FL'),(2139,381,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2140,381,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> Pre-season Rookies</h2>\r\nShowcase your skills alongside other All-American pre-season rookies.'),(2141,381,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2142,382,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory Preseason Tournament</h1>\r\nThis is your opportunity to play in front of All-America Game scouts. Our scouts will evaluate 2016 and 2017 grads for selection to the Under Armour All-America Game, which returns to historic Wrigley Field this summer.\r\n\r\nJanuary 16–18 / Cubs Park / Mesa, AZ'),(2143,382,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2144,382,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> Pre-season Tourney</h2>\r\n28 teams vie for this prestigious tournament championship.'),(2145,382,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2146,383,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory Preseason Tournament</h1>\r\nThis is your opportunity to play in front of All-America Game scouts. Our scouts will evaluate 2016 and 2017 grads for selection to the Under Armour All-America Game, which returns to historic Wrigley Field this summer.\r\n\r\nJanuary 16–18 / Cubs Park / Mesa, AZ'),(2147,383,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2148,383,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> Pre-season Tourney</h2>\r\n28 teams vie for this prestigious\r\ntournament championship.'),(2149,383,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2150,384,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory All-America Preseason Rookie Tournament</h1>\r\nJanuary 16-18 / Lake Myrtle Sports Complex / Auburndale, FL'),(2151,384,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2152,384,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour</strong> Pre-season Rookies</h2>\r\nShowcase your skills alongside other\r\nAll-American pre-season rookies.'),(2153,384,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2154,385,'_wp_attached_file','2014/10/bg-uabaseball.jpg'),(2155,385,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:4:{s:5:\"width\";i:1600;s:6:\"height\";i:840;s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"2014/10/bg-uabaseball.jpg\";s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(2156,13,'_thumbnail_id','385'),(2157,13,'page_excerpt',''),(2158,13,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2159,386,'_wp_attached_file','2014/10/bg-national-training.jpg'),(2160,386,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:4:{s:5:\"width\";i:1600;s:6:\"height\";i:840;s:4:\"file\";s:32:\"2014/10/bg-national-training.jpg\";s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(2161,65,'_thumbnail_id','386'),(2162,387,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction and personal attention from our experienced coaching staff that includes current and former professional players, college coaches, and pro scouts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to participate?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2163,387,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2164,387,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Training</h2>\r\nOur training camps offer intense instruction\r\nto enhance your game.'),(2165,387,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2166,388,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction and personal attention from our experienced coaching staff that includes current and former professional players, college coaches, and pro scouts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to participate?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2167,388,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2168,388,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Training</h2>\r\nOur training camps offer intense instruction\r\nto enhance your game.'),(2169,388,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2170,389,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour Baseball Factory\r\n<strong>National Training</strong></h1>\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory instructional camps offer you the chance to receive intensive instruction and personal attention from our experienced coaching staff that includes current and former professional players, college coaches, and pro scouts.\r\n\r\n<strong>Want to participate?</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Get started at the Under Armour Baseball Factory Tryout Tour.</strong>'),(2171,389,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2172,389,'page_excerpt','<h2><strong>Under Armour Baseball Factory</strong> National Training</h2>\r\nOur training camps offer intense instruction\r\nto enhance your game.'),(2173,389,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6'),(2174,390,'page_intro','<h1>Under Armour <strong>Baseball Factory</strong></h1>\r\nBaseball Factory and Under Armour have joined forces to discover and develop the best high school baseball players in the country.\r\n\r\nIt all starts at the <a href=\"http://fa.drxlrdev.com/events/\">Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour</a> where players are evaluated by our professional instructors. Top players are then invited to attend Under Armour Baseball Factory National Team, National Training, and All-America events. There they receive high-level instruction, compete against other top prospects, and play in front of college coaches.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#events\">Explore Opportunities</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(2175,390,'_page_intro','field_5465178d42959'),(2176,390,'page_excerpt',''),(2177,390,'_page_excerpt','field_546666ec96aa6');

/*Table structure for table `fawp_posts` */

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `fawp_posts`;

CREATE TABLE `fawp_posts` (
  `ID` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `post_author` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `post_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `post_date_gmt` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `post_content` longtext NOT NULL,
  `post_title` text NOT NULL,
  `post_excerpt` text NOT NULL,
  `post_status` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'publish',
  `comment_status` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'open',
  `ping_status` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'open',
  `post_password` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `post_name` varchar(200) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `to_ping` text NOT NULL,
  `pinged` text NOT NULL,
  `post_modified` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `post_modified_gmt` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `post_content_filtered` longtext NOT NULL,
  `post_parent` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `guid` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `menu_order` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `post_type` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'post',
  `post_mime_type` varchar(100) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `comment_count` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`ID`),
  KEY `post_name` (`post_name`),
  KEY `type_status_date` (`post_type`,`post_status`,`post_date`,`ID`),
  KEY `post_parent` (`post_parent`),
  KEY `post_author` (`post_author`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=392 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

/*Data for the table `fawp_posts` */

insert  into `fawp_posts`(`ID`,`post_author`,`post_date`,`post_date_gmt`,`post_content`,`post_title`,`post_excerpt`,`post_status`,`comment_status`,`ping_status`,`post_password`,`post_name`,`to_ping`,`pinged`,`post_modified`,`post_modified_gmt`,`post_content_filtered`,`post_parent`,`guid`,`menu_order`,`post_type`,`post_mime_type`,`comment_count`) values (1,1,'2014-09-17 20:12:29','2014-09-17 20:12:29','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2014-09-17 20:12:29','2014-09-17 20:12:29','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/site/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2014-09-17 20:12:29','2014-09-17 20:12:29','','Home','','publish','open','closed','','sample-page','','','2014-11-14 15:38:47','2014-11-14 15:38:47','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/site/?page_id=2',1,'page','',0),(4,1,'2014-10-01 20:32:22','2014-10-01 20:32:22','<h1>Your path to greatness \r\n<strong>starts here.</strong></h1>\r\nOver the last 20+ years, thousands of Baseball Factory players have made college teams and hundreds have played in the MLB, including Justin Verlander, CC Sabathia, and David Wright. All players get their start at an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout. Now it’s your turn to be discovered.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#events\">View Schedule of Events</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#\">Register Now</a></li>\r\n</ul>','Events','','publish','open','closed','','events','','','2014-11-14 15:36:33','2014-11-14 15:36:33','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=4',2,'page','',0),(5,1,'2014-10-01 20:32:22','2014-10-01 20:32:22','','Events','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-v1','','','2014-10-01 20:32:22','2014-10-01 20:32:22','',4,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(6,1,'2014-10-01 20:40:41','2014-10-01 20:40:41','Hi! I\'m the \"Events\" page','Events','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-v1','','','2014-10-01 20:40:41','2014-10-01 20:40:41','',4,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(12,4,'2014-10-14 02:00:57','2014-10-14 02:00:57','','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2014-10-14 02:00:57','2014-10-14 02:00:57','',2,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=12',0,'revision','',0),(13,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:16','2014-10-14 02:01:16','<h3><strong>More info on</strong> UA Baseball Factory</h3>\r\nSince 2007, Baseball Factory and Under Armour have helped hundreds of top players get discovered, get better, and get recruited. In 2014 alone, 5 of the top 8 players taken in the MLB draft were Under Armour Baseball Factory alum.\r\n<h3>Your path to greatness starts here.</h3>\r\n<strong>Want to be part of UA Baseball Factory?</strong> It all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour. You’ll be evaluated by our professional instructors and placed on the best development program to maximize your potential. Find a tryout near you and get started on your path to greatness.','Under Armour Baseball Factory','','publish','open','closed','','ua-baseball','','','2014-11-15 07:37:48','2014-11-15 07:37:48','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=13',3,'page','',0),(14,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:16','2014-10-14 02:01:16','','UA Baseball','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-10-14 02:01:16','2014-10-14 02:01:16','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=14',0,'revision','',0),(15,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:25','2014-10-14 02:01:25','','Player Development','','publish','open','closed','','player-development','','','2014-10-24 13:51:27','2014-10-24 13:51:27','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=15',4,'page','',0),(16,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:25','2014-10-14 02:01:25','','Player Development','','inherit','open','open','','15-revision-v1','','','2014-10-14 02:01:25','2014-10-14 02:01:25','',15,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=16',0,'revision','',0),(17,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:35','2014-10-14 02:01:35','','Baseball Factory TV','','publish','open','closed','','baseball-factory-tv','','','2014-10-24 13:51:35','2014-10-24 13:51:35','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=17',5,'page','',0),(18,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:35','2014-10-14 02:01:35','','Baseball Factory TV','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-v1','','','2014-10-14 02:01:35','2014-10-14 02:01:35','',17,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=18',0,'revision','',0),(19,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:42','2014-10-14 02:01:42','','Shop','','publish','open','closed','','shop','','','2014-10-24 13:51:39','2014-10-24 13:51:39','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=19',6,'page','',0),(20,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:42','2014-10-14 02:01:42','','Shop','','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-v1','','','2014-10-14 02:01:42','2014-10-14 02:01:42','',19,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=20',0,'revision','',0),(21,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:49','2014-10-14 02:01:49','<strong>Since 1994, we have helped more than 50,000 players get signed to a college team, more than 3,500 get drafted by a pro team, and more than 350 play for MLB teams.</strong> We achieve these results through a one-of-a-kind program that combines continued support and guidance before, during, and after each event a player attends with Baseball Factory.\r\n\r\nA player\'s first step with Baseball Factory is to be evaluated at an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour event. Once an evaluation is complete, we place that player in the appropriate development program. Players flow through our system in the same manner many young prospects move through the levels of a Major League organization (Rookie, A, AA, AAA, MLB). At each level, players are challenged both physically (through competition, high-level training,and accelerated techniques) and mentally (through Baseball IQ, life skills, and academic guidance) with the purpose of helping each player reach his full potential.\r\n\r\nBaseball Factory offers a unique, hands-on system for players who want to develop to their fullest capability–from academic specialists who know the ins and outs of the college admission process to some of the most sought-after instructors in the world who know how to bring out the very best in each player on the field to a marketing platform that has helped more players compete at the college baseball level than any other organization in America.','About','','publish','open','closed','','about','','','2014-11-14 16:27:30','2014-11-14 16:27:30','',0,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=21',7,'page','',0),(22,4,'2014-10-14 02:01:49','2014-10-14 02:01:49','','About','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-v1','','','2014-10-14 02:01:49','2014-10-14 02:01:49','',21,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=22',0,'revision','',0),(28,4,'2014-10-15 03:37:34','2014-10-15 03:37:34','<h2>Your path to greatnessstarts here.</h2>','Events','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-v1','','','2014-10-15 03:37:34','2014-10-15 03:37:34','',4,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=28',0,'revision','',0),(29,4,'2014-10-15 03:38:22','2014-10-15 03:38:22','<h1>Your path to greatness starts here.</h1>\r\nOver the last 20+ years, thousands of Baseball Factory players have made college teams and hundreds have played in the MLB, including Justin Verlander, CC Sabathia, and David Wright. All players get their start at an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout. Now it’s your turn to be discovered.','Events','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-v1','','','2014-10-15 03:38:22','2014-10-15 03:38:22','',4,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=29',0,'revision','',0),(30,4,'2014-10-15 03:38:48','2014-10-15 03:38:48','<h3>Your path to greatness starts here.</h3>\r\nOver the last 20+ years, thousands of Baseball Factory players have made college teams and hundreds have played in the MLB, including Justin Verlander, CC Sabathia, and David Wright. All players get their start at an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout. Now it’s your turn to be discovered.','Events','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-v1','','','2014-10-15 03:38:48','2014-10-15 03:38:48','',4,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=30',0,'revision','',0),(31,4,'2014-10-15 0