',0,'revision','',0),(48,4,'2014-10-24 13:53:21','2014-10-24 13:53:21','','The Top 100','','publish','open','closed','','the-top-100','','','2014-11-14 20:46:48','2014-11-14 20:46:48','',15,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=48',4,'page','',0),(49,4,'2014-10-24 13:53:21','2014-10-24 13:53:21','','The Top 100','','inherit','open','open','','48-revision-v1','','','2014-10-24 13:53:21','2014-10-24 13:53:21','',48,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=49',0,'revision','',0),(55,4,'2014-10-24 20:35:15','2014-10-24 20:35:15','<h1>UA <strong>Baseball Factory</strong></h1>\r\nBaseball Factory and Under Armour have joined forces to discover and develop the best high school baseball players in the country. \r\n\r\nIt all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour where players are evaluated by our professional instructors. Top players are then invited to attend National Team, National Training, and All-America events. There they receive high-level instruction, compete against other top prospects, and play in front of college coaches.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#events\">Explore Opportunities</a></li>\r\n</ul>','UA Baseball','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-10-24 20:35:15','2014-10-24 20:35:15','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=55',0,'revision','',0),(56,4,'2014-10-24 22:02:38','2014-10-24 22:02:38','','Temp Single Event Page','','publish','open','closed','','temp-single-event-page','','','2014-11-13 20:46:51','2014-11-13 20:46:51','',4,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=56',0,'page','',0),(57,4,'2014-10-24 22:02:38','2014-10-24 22:02:38','','Temp Single Event Page','','inherit','open','open','','56-revision-v1','','','2014-10-24 22:02:38','2014-10-24 22:02:38','',56,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=57',0,'revision','',0),(58,4,'2014-10-28 22:34:44','2014-10-28 22:34:44','<h1>UA <strong>Baseball Factory</strong></h1>\r\nBaseball Factory and Under Armour have joined forces to discover and develop the best high school baseball players in the country. \r\n\r\nIt all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour where players are evaluated by our professional instructors. Top players are then invited to attend National Team, National Training, and All-America events. There they receive high-level instruction, compete against other top prospects, and play in front of college coaches.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#events\">Explore Opportunities</a></li>\r\n</ul>','UA Baseball Factory','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-10-28 22:34:44','2014-10-28 22:34:44','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=58',0,'revision','',0),(63,4,'2014-10-31 20:18:16','2014-10-31 20:18:16','<h3>More About Our National Teams</h3>\r\nWith the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Teams, you get to learn from our coaches and share the field with other top high school prospects in competitive tournament play. In addition to these incredible on-the-field experiences, you learn important life skills to use in college and beyond.\r\n\r\nOnce you participate in an Under Armour Baseball Factory Team event, you’re part of our team until you graduate. We continue to provide guidance in your baseball skills development and become your trusted resource in navigating the college recruiting process.\r\n\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory National Teams are invitation only. To make a team, your first step is to be evaluated at a National Tryout Tour event. Once your evaluation is complete, we’ll place you on the best development program to maximize your success and set you on your path to greatness.','Under Armour Baseball Factory National Teams','','publish','open','open','','under-armour-baseball-factory-national-teams','','','2014-11-14 20:53:14','2014-11-14 20:53:14','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=63',1,'page','',0),(64,4,'2014-10-31 20:18:16','2014-10-31 20:18:16','','Under Armour National Team','','inherit','open','open','','63-revision-v1','','','2014-10-31 20:18:16','2014-10-31 20:18:16','',63,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=64',0,'revision','',0),(65,4,'2014-10-31 20:18:30','2014-10-31 20:18:30','<h3><strong>More About Our</strong> National Training</h3>\r\nBy working closely with our top-notch instructors and other serious athletes, you further develop your game for the next level. National Training events are designed to help you improve specific skills and create a plan for your continued growth and success. In addition to these beneficial experiences, you learn important life skills to use in college and beyond.\r\n\r\nOnce you participate in an Under Armour Baseball Factory Training event, you’re part of our team until you graduate. We continue to provide guidance in your baseball skills development and become your trusted resource in navigating the college recruiting process.\r\n\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory National Training events are invitation only. To receive an invitation, your first step is to be evaluated at a National Tryout Tour event. Once your evaluation is complete, we’ll place you on the best development program to maximize your success and set you on your path to greatness.','Under Armour Baseball Factory National Training','','publish','open','open','','under-armour-baseball-factory-national-training','','','2014-11-15 07:35:33','2014-11-15 07:35:33','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=65',2,'page','',0),(66,4,'2014-10-31 20:18:30','2014-10-31 20:18:30','','Under Armour National Training','','inherit','open','open','','65-revision-v1','','','2014-10-31 20:18:30','2014-10-31 20:18:30','',65,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=66',0,'revision','',0),(67,4,'2014-10-31 20:18:45','2014-10-31 20:18:45','2015 Under Armour All-America Game\r\n\r\nThe country’s best collection of top high school prospects converges on the historic confines of Wrigley Field for a weekend of intense competition, instruction, and national exposure.','Under Armour All-America Game','','publish','open','open','','ua-all-america-game','','','2014-11-14 20:54:19','2014-11-14 20:54:19','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=67',3,'page','',0),(68,4,'2014-10-31 20:18:45','2014-10-31 20:18:45','','UA All America Game','','inherit','open','open','','67-revision-v1','','','2014-10-31 20:18:45','2014-10-31 20:18:45','',67,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=68',0,'revision','',0),(69,4,'2014-10-31 20:21:38','2014-10-31 20:21:38','<h3>Elite Selection</h3>\r\nPlayers are selected to compete in this tournament based on a strong performance at a previous Baseball Factory event or recommendation by a pro scout. To be part of this tournament, your first step it to attend the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour. Find a tryout near you.\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n<h3>What You Get</h3>\r\nIn addition to competing against top talent from across the country, Baseball Factory Preseason All-Americans receive:\r\n\r\n<strong>Player Page:</strong> Your personalized webpage showcases professionally edited video from the event, as well as an evaluation from a pro scout. Share the link with friends, family and college coaches to gain additional exposure after the event.\r\n\r\n<strong>Recognition:</strong> Final rosters are displayed online and players rated as having \"Top Tools\" from the event receive special mention.\r\n\r\n<strong>World-Class Instruction:</strong> Our renowned coaches know how to bring out the very best in each and every athlete. Players work with our staff to maximize their on-field success.\r\n\r\n<strong>Spring Season Prep:</strong> By competing against other Baseball Factory Rookie Preseason All-Americans, players are better prepared to succeed during the upcoming spring season.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Under Armour Baseball Factory Preseason Tournament','','publish','open','open','','ua-pre-season-tournament','','','2014-11-14 20:59:43','2014-11-14 20:59:43','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=69',4,'page','',0),(70,4,'2014-10-31 20:21:38','2014-10-31 20:21:38','','UA Pre-season Tournament','','inherit','open','open','','69-revision-v1','','','2014-10-31 20:21:38','2014-10-31 20:21:38','',69,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=70',0,'revision','',0),(71,4,'2014-10-31 20:21:47','2014-10-31 20:21:47','<h3>Elite Selection</h3>\r\nPlayers are selected to compete in this tournament based on a strong performance at a previous Baseball Factory event or recommendation by a pro scout. To be part of this tournament, your first step it to attend the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour. Find a tryout near you.\r\n<h3>What You Get</h3>\r\nIn addition to competing against top talent from across the country, Baseball Factory Rookie Preseason All-Americans receive:\r\n\r\n<strong>Player Page:</strong> Your personalized webpage showcases professionally edited video from the event, as well as an evaluation from a pro scout. Share the link with friends, family and college coaches to gain additional exposure after the event.\r\n\r\n<strong>Recognition:</strong> Final rosters are displayed online and players rated as having \"Top Tools\" from the event receive special mention.\r\n\r\n<strong>World-Class Instruction:</strong> Our renowned coaches know how to bring out the very best in each and every athlete. Players work with our staff to maximize their on-field success.\r\n\r\n<strong>Spring Season Prep:</strong> By competing against other Baseball Factory Rookie Preseason All-Americans, players are better prepared to succeed during the upcoming spring season.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Under Armour Baseball Factory Preseason Rookies','','publish','open','open','','ua-rookie-preseason','','','2014-11-14 21:00:34','2014-11-14 21:00:34','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?page_id=71',5,'page','',0),(72,4,'2014-10-31 20:21:47','2014-10-31 20:21:47','','UA Rookie Preseason','','inherit','open','open','','71-revision-v1','','','2014-10-31 20:21:47','2014-10-31 20:21:47','',71,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/?p=72',0,'revision','',0),(73,4,'2014-10-31 20:28:22','2014-10-31 20:28:22','','About BBF','','publish','open','open'