<h3>Your path to greatness starts here.</h3>\n			<p><strong>Want to be part of UA Baseball Factory?</strong> It all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour. You’ll be evaluated by our professional instructors and placed on the best development program to maximize your potential. Find a tryout near you and get started on your path to greatness. </p>','UA Baseball Factory','','inherit','open','open','','13-autosave-v1','','','2014-11-13 21:07:06','2014-11-13 21:07:06','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/13-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(323,4,'2014-11-13 21:07:29','2014-11-13 21:07:29','<h3><span>More info on</span> UA Baseball Factory</h3>\r\n			<p>Since 2007, Baseball Factory and Under Armour have helped hundreds of top players get discovered, get better, and get recruited. In 2014 alone, 5 of the top 8 players taken in the MLB draft were Under Armour Baseball Factory alum.</p>\r\n			<h3>Your path to greatness starts here.</h3>\r\n			<p><strong>Want to be part of UA Baseball Factory?</strong> It all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour. You’ll be evaluated by our professional instructors and placed on the best development program to maximize your potential. Find a tryout near you and get started on your path to greatness. </p>','UA Baseball Factory','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-11-13 21:07:29','2014-11-13 21:07:29','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(324,4,'2014-11-13 21:21:52','2014-11-13 21:21:52','<h3><span>More info on</span> UA Baseball Factory</h3>More About Our\nNational Teams\n\nWith the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Teams, you get to learn from our coaches and share the field with other top high school prospects in competitive tournament play. In addition to these incredible on-the-field experiences, you learn important life skills to use in college and beyond. \n\nOnce you participate in an Under Armour Baseball Factory Team event, you’re part of our team until you graduate. We continue to provide guidance in your baseball skills development and become your trusted resource in navigating the college recruiting process. \n\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory National Teams are invitation only. To make a team, your first step is to be evaluated at a National Tryout Tour event. Once your evaluation is complete, we’ll place you on the best development program to maximize your success and set you on your path to greatness.','Under Armour National Teams','Get top-level coaching and compete on our tournament teams.','inherit','open','open','','63-autosave-v1','','','2014-11-13 21:21:52','2014-11-13 21:21:52','',63,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/63-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(325,4,'2014-11-13 21:09:43','2014-11-13 21:09:43','','Under Armour National Teams','','inherit','open','open','','63-revision-v1','','','2014-11-13 21:09:43','2014-11-13 21:09:43','',63,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/63-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(326,4,'2014-11-13 21:10:02','2014-11-13 21:10:02','<h3><span>More info on</span> UA Baseball Factory</h3>\r\n			<p>Since 2007, Baseball Factory and Under Armour have helped hundreds of top players get discovered, get better, and get recruited. In 2014 alone, 5 of the top 8 players taken in the MLB draft were Under Armour Baseball Factory alum.</p>\r\n			<h3>Your path to greatness starts here.</h3>\r\n			<p><strong>Want to be part of UA Baseball Factory?</strong> It all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour. You’ll be evaluated by our professional instructors and placed on the best development program to maximize your potential. Find a tryout near you and get started on your path to greatness. </p>','UA Baseball Factory','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-11-13 21:10:02','2014-11-13 21:10:02','',13,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(327,4,'2014-11-13 21:14:11','2014-11-13 21:14:11','<h3><span>More info on</span> UA Baseball 