14 15:49:57','<strong>Since 1994, we have helped more than 50,000 players get signed to a college team, more than 3,500 get drafted by a pro team, and more than 350 play for MLB teams.</strong> We achieve these results through a one-of-a-kind program that combines continued support and guidance before, during, and after each event a player attends with Baseball Factory.\n\nA player\'s first step with Baseball Factory is to be evaluated at an Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour event. Once an evaluation is complete, we place that player in the appropriate development program. Players flow through our system in the same manner many young prospects move through the levels of a Major League organization (Rookie, A, AA, AAA, MLB). At each level, players are challenged both physically (through competition, high-level training,and accelerated techniques) and mentally (through Baseball IQ, life skills, and academic guidance) with the purpose of helping each player reach his full potential.\n\nBaseball Factory offers a unique, hands-on system for players who want to develop to their fullest capability–from academic specialists who know the ins and outs of the college admission process to some of the most sought-after instructors in the world who know how to bring out the very best in each player on the field to a marketing platform that has helped more players compete at the college baseball level than any other organization in America.','About','','inherit','open','open','','21-autosave-v1','','','2014-11-14 15:49:57','2014-11-14 15:49:57','',21,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/21-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(349,4,'2014-11-14 16:02:52','2014-11-14 16:02:52','<strong>Since 1994, we have helped more than 50,000 players get signed to a college team, more than 3,500 get drafted by a pro team, and more than 350 play for MLB teams.</strong> We achieve these results through a one-of-a-kind program that combines continued support and guidance before, during, and after e