\n<h3>Your path to greatness starts here.</h3>\r\n<strong>Want to be part of UA Baseball Factory?</strong> It all starts at the Under Armour Baseball Factory National Tryout Tour. You’ll be evaluated by our professional instructors and placed on the best development program to maximize your potential. Find a tryout near you and get started on your path to greatness.','Alumni','','inherit','open','open','','83-revision-v1','','','2014-11-14 17:21:58','2014-11-14 17:21:58','',83,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/83-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(364,4,'2014-11-14 20:29:54','2014-11-14 20:29:54','<h3>More About Our National Training</h3>\r\nBy working closely with our top-notch instructors and other serious athletes, you further develop your game for the next level. National Training events are designed to help you improve specific skills and create a plan for your continued growth and success. In addition to these beneficial experiences, you learn important life skills to use in college and beyond.\r\n\r\nOnce you participate in an Under Armour Baseball Factory Training event, you’re part of our team until you graduate. We continue to provide guidance in your baseball skills development and become your trusted resource in navigating the college recruiting process.\r\n\r\nUnder Armour Baseball Factory National Training events are invitation only. To receive an invitation, your first step is to be evaluated at a National Tryout Tour event. Once your evaluation is complete, we’ll place you on the best development program to maximize your success and set you on your path to greatness.','<span>Under Armour Baseball Factory</span> National Training','Our training camps offer intense instruction to enhance your game.','inherit','open','open','','65-revision-v1','','','2014-11-14 20:29:54','2014-11-14 20:29:54','',65,'http://fa.drxlrdev.com/65-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(365,4,'2014-11-14 20:30:38','2014-11-14 20:30:38','<h3>More About Our National Training</h3>\r\nBy working 